# Admin feature

- All `/admin/*` routes require portal session + `canAccessDocsAdmin` (`requireDocsAdmin` in `+layout.server.ts`)
- Fixed left sidebar via `AdminSidebar.svelte`; page content uses `AdminHeader.svelte`
- Multi-field forms: `AdminFormTable` + 4-column invisible table (see `admin-form-table` rule/skill)
- Document sort order: drag-and-drop on dashboard (`DocumentOrderPanel`), not in document editor forms
- Documents live at `/admin/documents`, editor at `/admin/documents/[id]`, create at `/admin/documents/new`
- Form actions validate with Zod schemas from `$lib/schemas/`; return `fail(400, { errors })`
- Sign out: `POST /api/auth/logout`, redirect `/`
- CodeMirror editor: manual save only (no autosave)
